_sText: This is my first map I've ever made for CS:S, and the first map I've ever made in general for the Source-Engine. It is a warehouse, as the title says. I haven't done anything with the lightning, and there are no props on the map. I do realise it needs a better Skybox too, but I can't do anything as the file is lost as I've gotten a new harddrive since I made this map.
